data.value: This game is a puzzle game. There are 3 stages of passing. The first stage is with simple squares .You need to match 3 or more objects by exchanging two pieces. On every 10 seconds the matched pieces will disappear and then will be generated the new group of pieces. The exchanging of two pieces is consisted of clicking with the left button on the mouse and then choose another which is one row up or down or is one column on left or right, also with clicking on the left button. When you click on the first piece, it is selected and then when you click on the second piece, if they are neighbors they will change their places.
